### Tenancy Requirements

- Always accept `(tenant: str, workspace: str)` in tools/services.
- Use [tenancy/context.py](mdc:src/ultimate_discord_intelligence_bot/tenancy/context.py) for context and namespacing.
- Separate data storage by tenant/workspace to prevent leakage.

### Good Practices

- Thread tenant context through async tasks and background jobs.
- Include tenant/workspace in cache keys, metrics, and logs.
